OL,3,CWhy are foreign criminals being paid
OL,4,Cto leave the UK?
OL,6,FBy ITV News Producer Hannah Ward-
OL,7,FGlenton
OL,9,FConvicted sex offender Hadush Kebatu
OL,10,Fwas given #500 when he was deported
OL,11,Ffrom the UK on Tuesday night.
OL,13,FHe arrived in Ethiopia on Wednesday
OL,14,Fmorning, with no right to return to
OL,15,Fthe UK, according to the Home Office.
OL,17,FBut why was a criminal given money to
OL,18,Fleave the UK? ITV News explains.
OL,20,FHow do criminals leave the UK?
