OL,3,CWhy are foreign criminals being paid
OL,4,Cto leave the UK?
OL,6,FAs part of the facilitated return
OL,7,Fscheme, the offenders receive
OL,8,Ffinancial support to encourage them to
OL,9,Fcooperate with their removal.
OL,11,FAlong with the facilitated return
OL,12,Fscheme, there is also voluntary return
OL,13,Ffor migrants who have not been
OL,14,Fconvicted of a crime. This gives
OL,15,Fmigrants in the UK support to return
OL,16,Fhome if they meet certain criteria,
OL,17,Fsuch as by being in the UK illegally,
OL,18,Foverstaying a visa, or having made a
OL,19,Fclaim for asylum which was rejected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
