OL,3,CWhy are foreign criminals being paid
OL,4,Cto leave the UK?
OL,6,FPeople eligible for voluntary return
OL,7,Fare also able to access financial
OL,8,Fsupport from the UK government.
OL,10,FPeople who are subject to enforced
OL,11,Fremoval from the UK are not typically
OL,12,Foffered any money, but each person is
OL,13,Fjudged on a case by case basis.
OL,15,FDeportation flights take off several
OL,16,Ftimes a week from Britain. Last year
OL,17,Fover 5,000 foreign national offenders
OL,18,Fwere deported, a rise on the year
OL,19,Fbefore.
