OL,11,FWhich offenders are eligible to be
OL,12,Freturned to their home country?
OL,14,FAny foreign national offender could be
OL,15,Feligible for the facilitated return
OL,16,Fscheme if they fulfill the criteria -
OL,17,Fthat includes anybody with a British
OL,18,FOverseas Citizen passport, British
OL,19,FNational Overseas passport or any
OL,20,Fother non-British citizen passport.
