OL,3,CWhy are foreign criminals being paid
OL,4,Cto leave the UK?
OL,6,FBritish citizens are exempt from the
OL,7,Ffacilitated return scheme.
OL,9,FParticipation in the scheme is
OL,10,Fvoluntary, but it does not replace
OL,11,Fenforcement action. All departures
OL,12,Fmust comply with UK law and
OL,13,Finternational obligations.
OL,15,FApplications are reviewed by a
OL,16,Fdedicated Home Office team, with
OL,17,Fstricter checks for serious offences.
OL,19,FAcceptance can be withdrawn if someone
OL,20,Ffails to comply with the rules or
OL,21,Fcauses delays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
