OL,3,CWhy are foreign criminals being paid
OL,4,Cto leave the UK?
OL,6,FHow much money can foreign national
OL,7,Foffenders receive?
OL,9,FAll foreign national offenders are
OL,10,Feligible to receive money as part of
OL,11,Fthe facilitated return scheme.
OL,13,FThe amount of money they receive
OL,14,Fdepends on whether or not they receive
OL,15,Fa prison sentence, and if so, whether
OL,16,Fthey are still serving that sentence
OL,17,For if they have completed their
OL,18,Fsentence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
