OL,3,CWhy are foreign criminals being paid
OL,4,Cto leave the UK?
OL,6,FIf they apply while they are still in
OL,7,Fcustody, they can receive more money -
OL,8,Fthis is to try and encourage people to
OL,9,Fleave earlier.
OL,11,FThe Home Office lists the following
OL,12,Fgrants as being available under
OL,13,Fcertain circumstances:
OL,15,FAdditional #500
