OL,3,CWhy are foreign criminals being paid
OL,4,Cto leave the UK?
OL,6,FIf a person meets the criteria for
OL,7,Fvoluntary return, they may receive up
OL,8,Fto #3,000 in financial support. This
OL,9,Fis different to the facilitated return
OL,10,Fscheme in that people who apply for it
OL,11,Fare not convicted criminals.
OL,13,FHadush Kebatu, who was wrongly freed
OL,14,Ffrom HMP Chelmsford on Friday morning
OL,15,Finstead of being sent to an
OL,16,Fimmigration detention centre, had
OL,17,Fapplied for the facilitated return
OL,18,Fscheme, but that application was
OL,19,Frejected, Downing Street said on
OL,20,FWednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
