OL,3,CWhy are foreign criminals being paid
OL,4,Cto leave the UK?
OL,6,FHe was instead offered a #500
OL,7,F"discretionary payment" after
OL,8,Fthreatening to disrupt his deportation.
OL,10,FIt is understood the payment was an
OL,11,Foperational decision made by the
OL,12,Fremoval team as an alternative to the
OL,13,Fslower and more expensive process of
OL,14,Ffurther detaining Kebatu and putting
OL,15,Fhim on a new flight, which could have
OL,16,Ffaced a legal challenge.
