OL,3,CWhy are foreign criminals being paid
OL,4,Cto leave the UK?
OL,6,FThe UK Home Office funds the
OL,7,Ffacilitated returns scheme.
OL,8,FIndirectly, the money comes from
OL,9,Fpublic money, as the Home Office is
OL,10,Fsupported by taxpayer money.
OL,12,FHow do offenders receive the money?
OL,14,FForeign national offenders receive the
OL,15,Ffull amount of money on a pre-paid
OL,16,Fcard that can used when they have left
OL,17,Fthe UK.
OL,19,FWhy are foreign national offenders
OL,20,Fgiven money?
