OL,3,CWhy are foreign criminals being paid
OL,4,Cto leave the UK?
OL,6,FThe government says foreign national
OL,7,Foffenders are expected to use the
OL,8,Fmoney "to actively reintegrate into
OL,9,Flife" in their home country.
OL,11,FIt says the resettlement grant should
OL,12,Fbe put towards "meaningful activities
OL,13,Faimed at creating a stable, settled
OL,14,Flife in the country of return".
OL,16,FIt suggests setting up a business,
OL,17,Fpartnership or buying into an existing
OL,18,Fbusiness, education or vocational
OL,19,Fstudies, housing or medical expenses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
