OL,3,CWhy are foreign criminals being paid
OL,4,Cto leave the UK?
OL,6,FThe government has said it is cheaper
OL,7,Fin the longer term to provide these
OL,8,Fpayments instead of detaining foreign
OL,9,Fnational offenders.
OL,11,FIn an interview with ITV News in
OL,12,FSeptember, Home Secretary Shabana
OL,13,FMahmood said a voluntary removal "is
OL,14,Factually cheaper for the British
OL,15,Ftaxpayer".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
